   * Gets the value of the given path.
   *
   * @example
   * xapi.status
   *   .get('Audio Volume')
   *   .then((volume) => { console.log(volume); });

   * @example
   * xapi.config
   *   .get('Audio DefaultVolume')
   *   .then((volume) => { console.log(volume); });
   *
   * @param {string} path - Path to configuration node.
   * @return {Promise} - Resolved to the configuration value when ready.
